DOC.TE:
   The Dodgers' move from Channel 5 to Channel 13 is not a good thing
for most Dodger fans in the Coachella Valley. Time Warner Cable,
which dominates the area, does not carry Channel 13.

   In addition to his son, Burrell is survived by his wife, Clara;
son Mark of Anaheim Hills; five grandchildren; one great-grandchild;
and a sister, Faith Martin.

   Survivors include his wife, Marjory Graff McGuire, whom he married
in 1945, of Gaithersburg; a daughter, Joan McGuire of Raleigh, N.C.;
a brother; and a sister.
